"name, to avoid collision with existing (and future) extensions. For "
"example, a hypothetic extension to handle `Google Sitemaps`_ would use "
"settings like ``GOOGLESITEMAP_ENABLED``, ``GOOGLESITEMAP_DEPTH``, and so "
"on."
